707267f-a.title: Brooklyn: Warren St. - Court St.
707267f-a.text:
Warren Street, east from Court Street. On the west side
of the street, directly beyond the truck, is the Warren Street
Methodist Episcopal Church, near Smith Street.
VView 2 is in the same direction, seen from the center of
the block.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: June 6, 1933
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: July 1, 1935
